B.NF=new A.ac("The Fool","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udccf","New beginnings, spontaneity, and a free spirit. You are on the verge of an exciting, unexpected journey.","Recklessness, risk-taking without thought, or holding back out of fear. Look before you leap.")
B.Ni=new A.ac("The Magician","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udfa9","Manifestation, resourcefulness, and willpower. You have all the tools you need to succeed \u2014 use them.","Manipulation, poor planning, or untapped potential. Skills may be going to waste.")
B.N2=new A.ac("The High Priestess","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udf19","Intuition, mystery, and inner knowledge. Trust your gut and look beyond the surface.","Secrets, disconnection from intuition, or hidden agendas. Something is being concealed.")
B.Nm=new A.ac("The Empress","Major Arcana","\ud83d\udc51","Fertility, abundance, and nurturing energy. A time of creativity, growth, and beauty.","Creative block, dependence, or neglect. You may be smothering someone or feeling smothered.")
B.Nh=new A.ac("The Emperor","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f","Authority, structure, and stability. Strong leadership and a solid foundation guide you now.","Domination, rigidity, or lack of discipline. Power may be misused or structure may be crumbling.")
B.NI=new A.ac("The Hierophant","Major Arcana","\u26ea","Tradition, conformity, and spiritual wisdom. Seek guidance from established institutions or mentors.","Rebellion, subversiveness, or breaking from convention. Question the rules you have been given.")
B.NL=new A.ac("The Lovers","Major Arcana","\u2764\ufe0f","Love, harmony, and alignment of values. A meaningful relationship or an important choice lies ahead.","Disharmony, imbalance, or misaligned values. A relationship may be tested or a decision avoided.")
B.Np=new A.ac("The Chariot","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udfc6","Determination, control, and victory. Harness your willpower to overcome obstacles and forge ahead.","Lack of control, aggression, or feeling directionless. You may be forcing things that are not ready.")
B.NG=new A.ac("Strength","Major Arcana","\ud83e\udd81","Courage, patience, and inner strength. True power comes from compassion and quiet confidence.","Self-doubt, weakness, or raw emotion taking over. You may be struggling with inner demons.")
B.ND=new A.ac("The Hermit","Major Arcana","\ud83d\udd6f\ufe0f","Soul-searching, introspection, and solitude. Withdraw from the noise to find your inner truth.","Isolation, loneliness, or withdrawal from the world. You may be hiding or refusing guidance.")
B.NR=new A.ac("Wheel of Fortune","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udfa1","Good luck, karma, and life cycles. The wheel is turning in your favor \u2014 embrace the change.","Bad luck, resistance to change, or breaking cycles. Fate may feel out of your control.")
B.N3=new A.ac("Justice","Major Arcana","\u2696\ufe0f","Fairness, truth, and the law of cause and effect. An honest outcome will prevail.","Unfairness, dishonesty, or avoiding accountability. The truth may be obscured or justice delayed.")
B.NE=new A.ac("The Hanged Man","Major Arcana","\ud83d\ude43","Pause, surrender, and new perspectives. Letting go and seeing things differently will bring enlightenment.","Stalling, resistance, or martyrdom. You may be delaying the inevitable or clinging to old ways.")
B.NS=new A.ac("Death","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udf11","Endings, transformation, and transition. Something must end for something new and better to begin.","Resistance to change, stagnation, or a slow painful transition. Let go of what no longer serves you.")
B.Nu=new A.ac("Temperance","Major Arcana","\u2697\ufe0f","Balance, moderation, and patience. Take the middle path and blend opposing forces with grace.","Imbalance, excess, or lack of long-term vision. Things may feel out of sync or extreme.")
B.Nz=new A.ac("The Devil","Major Arcana","\ud83d\ude08","Bondage, addiction, and materialism. You may feel trapped by unhealthy attachments or limiting beliefs.","Breaking free, reclaiming power, or detachment. You are releasing yourself from a harmful bond.")
B.Nv=new A.ac("The Tower","Major Arcana","\u26a1","Sudden upheaval, chaos, and revelation. A shocking event shatters illusions and clears the way for truth.","Avoiding disaster, fear of change, or delaying the inevitable collapse. The storm is coming regardless.")
B.N8=new A.ac("The Star","Major Arcana","\u2b50","Hope, inspiration, and serenity. After hardship comes renewal \u2014 trust that the universe has a plan.","Despair, lack of faith, or disconnection. You may have lost hope or feel abandoned by the universe.")
B.Nw=new A.ac("The Moon","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udf15","Illusion, fear, and the unconscious. Not everything is as it seems \u2014 trust your instincts in the dark.","Confusion lifting, releasing fear, or uncovering deception. The fog is beginning to clear.")
B.N0=new A.ac("The Sun","Major Arcana","\u2600\ufe0f","Joy, success, and vitality. A radiant period of positivity, clarity, and achievement is upon you.","Temporary sadness, inner child wounds, or pessimism. The light is still there \u2014 look harder.")
B.O6=new A.ac("Judgement","Major Arcana","\ud83d\udcef","Reflection, reckoning, and awakening. A moment of clarity calls you to rise and embrace your true self.","Self-doubt, refusal of self-examination, or ignoring the call. You may be judging yourself too harshly.")
B.Nr=new A.ac("The World","Major Arcana","\ud83c\udf0d","Completion, integration, and accomplishment. A cycle ends in triumph \u2014 celebrate how far you have come.","Incompletion, shortcuts, or a lack of closure. You may be close to the finish line but stalling.")
B.Ng=new A.ac("Ace of Cups","Cups","\ud83e\udd42","New love, emotional beginnings, and compassion. Your heart is open to receive deep emotional gifts.","Emotional loss, blocked feelings, or emptiness. You may be closed off from love or grieving.")
B.O8=new A.ac("Two of Cups","Cups","\ud83d\udc9e","Partnership, mutual attraction, and connection. A meaningful bond is forming or deepening.","Imbalance in a relationship, miscommunication, or a broken bond. Something is off between two people.")
B.N4=new A.ac("Three of Cups","Cups","\ud83c\udf89","Celebration, friendship, and community. Gather with those you love and revel in shared joy.","Overindulgence, gossip, or social isolation. A group dynamic may be turning toxic.")
B.Ns=new A.ac("Four of Cups","Cups","\ud83e\uddd8","Contemplation, apathy, and missed opportunities. You may be so withdrawn that gifts go unnoticed.","Motivation returning, new perspective, or seizing an opportunity. Emerging from a period of withdrawal.")
B.NB=new A.ac("Five of Cups","Cups","\ud83d\ude22","Loss, regret, and disappointment. Grief is real, but do not overlook what still remains.","Acceptance, moving on, or forgiveness. You are beginning to heal from past pain.")
B.NM=new A.ac("Six of Cups","Cups","\ud83c\udf38","Nostalgia, childhood memories, and innocence. A connection to the past brings warmth or reunion.","Stuck in the past, unrealistic nostalgia, or leaving home behind. It is time to move forward.")
B.N9=new A.ac("Seven of Cups","Cups","\ud83c\udf08","Fantasy, illusion, and wishful thinking. Many options appear before you, but not all are what they seem.","Clarity, decisiveness, or disillusionment. The fog is lifting and reality sets in.")
B.Od=new A.ac("Eight of Cups","Cups","\ud83d\udeb6","Walking away, disillusionment, and seeking deeper meaning. Leaving behind what no longer fulfills you.","Fear of moving on, hopelessness, or staying in a bad situation. It is hard to let go.")
B.NN=new A.ac("Nine of Cups","Cups","\ud83d\ude0a","Contentment, satisfaction, and wishes fulfilled. Emotional abundance and personal happiness are yours.","Greed, dissatisfaction, or a wish unfulfilled. Inner happiness may be lacking despite outward success.")
B.NW=new A.ac("Ten of Cups","Cups","\ud83c\udfe0","Harmony, happiness, and family bliss. Emotional fulfillment and lasting love surround you.","Family conflict, broken home, or misaligned values. True harmony requires deeper work.")
B.Oc=new A.ac("Page of Cups","Cups","\ud83d\udc1f","Creative opportunities, curiosity, and an open heart. Embrace the unexpected and let imagination lead.","Emotional immaturity, creative blocks, or naivety. Someone may be acting out of emotional insecurity.")
B.NA=new A.ac("Knight of Cups","Cups","\ud83e\udd0d","Romance, charm, and following the heart. An invitation or opportunity arrives with emotional appeal.","Moodiness, unrealistic expectations, or jealousy. Emotions may be driving poor decisions.")
B.Ny=new A.ac("Queen of Cups","Cups","\ud83c\udf0a","Compassion, calm, and emotional intelligence. A deeply empathic presence who offers nurturing support.","Emotional insecurity, co-dependency, or martyrdom. Emotions are overwhelming rather than guiding.")
B.Nx=new A.ac("King of Cups","Cups","\ud83c\udf0a","Emotional balance, generosity, and wisdom. A calm and compassionate leader who masters feelings.","Emotional manipulation, moodiness, or volatility. Someone may be using emotions as a weapon.")
B.O7=new A.ac("Ace of Wands","Wands","\ud83d\udd25","Inspiration, new beginnings, and creative potential. A spark of passion ignites a new venture.","Delays, lack of motivation, or a false start. The fire is there but hard to get going.")
B.Nc=new A.ac("Two of Wands","Wands","\ud83c\udf10","Planning, future vision, and progress. You are mapping out your path and seeing a world of possibility.","Fear of the unknown, poor planning, or playing it too safe. Do not let fear keep you home.")
B.O3=new A.ac("Three of Wands","Wands","\ud83d\udea2","Expansion, foresight, and long-term success. Your plans are underway \u2014 watch for opportunity on the horizon.","Delays, obstacles, or lack of foresight. Progress may be slower than expected.")
B.NX=new A.ac("Four of Wands","Wands","\ud83c\udf8a","Celebration, harmony, and homecoming. A milestone is reached and community comes together to rejoice.","Instability, lack of support, or a celebration marred by conflict. Something disrupts the harmony.")
B.N1=new A.ac("Five of Wands","Wands","\u2694\ufe0f","Conflict, competition, and tension. A clash of ideas or ambitions creates friction \u2014 channel it productively.","Avoiding conflict, internal struggle, or competition turning nasty. Choose your battles wisely.")
B.O_=new A.ac("Six of Wands","Wands","\ud83c\udfc5","Victory, success, and public recognition. Your efforts are being noticed and rewarded \u2014 enjoy the spotlight.","Egotism, fall from grace, or private victory. Recognition may not come, or may come at a cost.")
B.N7=new A.ac("Seven of Wands","Wands","\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","Perseverance, defense, and holding your ground. Stand firm in your beliefs even under pressure.","Giving up, feeling overwhelmed, or being on the defensive. Pick your battles carefully.")
B.N6=new A.ac("Eight of Wands","Wands","\ud83d\udca8","Speed, momentum, and rapid change. Things are moving fast \u2014 stay focused and go with the flow.","Delays, frustration, or scattered energy. Plans may stall or communication breaks down.")
B.Nb=new A.ac("Nine of Wands","Wands","\ud83e\ude79","Resilience, courage, and persistence. You are almost there \u2014 do not give up now, even if weary.","Exhaustion, defensiveness, or giving up at the last hurdle. Guard against paranoia or burnout.")
B.NH=new A.ac("Ten of Wands","Wands","\ud83d\ude13","Burden, responsibility, and hard work. You are carrying a heavy load \u2014 consider what you can delegate.","Release of burden, delegation, or collapsing under pressure. Time to set something down.")
B.NZ=new A.ac("Page of Wands","Wands","\ud83c\udf31","Enthusiasm, exploration, and discovery. A free spirit eager to learn and begin new adventures.","Immaturity, lack of direction, or hasty actions. Energy without focus leads nowhere.")
B.NP=new A.ac("Knight of Wands","Wands","\ud83d\udc0e","Action, adventure, and fearlessness. A bold, passionate charge toward your goals with burning ambition.","Recklessness, impulsiveness, or scattered energy. Passion without a plan causes chaos.")
B.NY=new A.ac("Queen of Wands","Wands","\ud83c\udf3b","Courage, confidence, and determination. A fiery, magnetic presence who pursues life with bold enthusiasm.","Jealousy, selfishness, or demanding behavior. The fire may be burning others rather than inspiring them.")
B.NO=new A.ac("King of Wands","Wands","\ud83e\udd81","Leadership, vision, and entrepreneurship. A bold visionary who leads by example with passion and purpose.","Impulsiveness, arrogance, or high expectations. A domineering style may be alienating others.")
B.O1=new A.ac("Ace of Swords","Swords","\u2694\ufe0f","Clarity, breakthrough, and sharp truth. A moment of mental clarity cuts through confusion and illusion.","Confusion, brutality, or clouded judgment. The truth may be painful or difficult to accept.")
B.O9=new A.ac("Two of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\ude48","Indecision, stalemate, and avoidance. You may be blocking information to avoid making a hard choice.","Indecision broken, truth revealed, or overwhelming information. The blindfold is removed.")
B.Nj=new A.ac("Three of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\udc94","Heartbreak, sorrow, and grief. Pain is real and must be felt \u2014 allow yourself to mourn and heal.","Recovery, forgiveness, and releasing pain. Healing is underway, even if slowly.")
B.NU=new A.ac("Four of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\udca4","Rest, recovery, and contemplation. Step back from the chaos to restore your strength and clarity.","Restlessness, burnout, or refusing to rest. The body and mind demand a break you keep denying.")
B.NK=new A.ac("Five of Swords","Swords","\ud83c\udff3\ufe0f","Conflict, defeat, and winning at a cost. Even in victory, something is lost \u2014 consider the price.","Reconciliation, moving past conflict, or lingering resentment. Wounds may still be raw.")
B.O2=new A.ac("Six of Swords","Swords","\u26f5","Transition, moving on, and calmer waters. You are leaving behind turbulence and heading toward peace.","Resistance to change, unfinished business, or rough waters. The journey forward is complicated.")
B.O4=new A.ac("Seven of Swords","Swords","\ud83e\udd8a","Deception, strategy, and getting away with something. Cunning may be needed \u2014 or someone is being sneaky.","Coming clean, rethinking strategy, or being caught. Secrets may surface now.")
B.Nf=new A.ac("Eight of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\udd78\ufe0f","Restriction, feeling trapped, and self-imposed limitations. The prison you are in may be of your own making.","Freedom, releasing limiting beliefs, or escaping a bad situation. You are finding a way out.")
B.O5=new A.ac("Nine of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\ude28","Anxiety, nightmares, and dark thoughts. Worry is at its peak \u2014 remember, fear often exceeds reality.","Hope emerging, releasing anxiety, or reaching rock bottom. Things can only go up from here.")
B.Nt=new A.ac("Ten of Swords","Swords","\ud83c\udf05","Painful endings, betrayal, and rock bottom. A dramatic conclusion, but every ending is a new dawn.","Recovery, resisting an inevitable end, or surviving the worst. Rising from the ashes is possible.")
B.Nl=new A.ac("Page of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\udd0d","Curiosity, vigilance, and quick thinking. A sharp mind hungry for information and new ideas.","Gossip, haste, or all talk and no action. Ideas abound but follow-through is lacking.")
B.O0=new A.ac("Knight of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\udca8","Ambition, speed, and direct action. Charging forward with sharp focus and fearless determination.","Recklessness, verbal aggression, or rushing in without thinking. Slow down or cause damage.")
B.N_=new A.ac("Queen of Swords","Swords","\u2744\ufe0f","Clear boundaries, honest communication, and sharp intellect. Truth-telling with compassion and wisdom.","Cold-heartedness, cruelty, or bitter judgments. Pain may have turned to hardness.")
B.NT=new A.ac("King of Swords","Swords","\ud83d\udc41\ufe0f","Authority, intellect, and clear thinking. A master of reason who rules with logic, fairness, and truth.","Manipulation, abuse of power, or cold rationality without empathy. A tyrant of the mind.")
B.NC=new A.ac("Ace of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83d\udcb0","New financial opportunity, abundance, and manifestation. A prosperous beginning in material matters.","Missed opportunity, poor financial planning, or greed. A chance for prosperity may be slipping away.")
B.Oa=new A.ac("Two of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83e\udd39","Balance, adaptability, and time management. Juggling multiple priorities \u2014 keep your sense of humor.","Imbalance, disorganization, or overwhelm. Too many balls in the air and something is about to drop.")
B.No=new A.ac("Three of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f","Teamwork, learning, and skill-building. Collaboration and mastery lead to lasting achievement.","Lack of teamwork, mediocrity, or poor planning. Egos may be getting in the way of progress.")
B.NV=new A.ac("Four of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udfe6","Security, conservation, and control. Holding tightly to what you have \u2014 but at what cost?","Greed, materialism, or release of control. Either clinging too hard or finally letting go.")
B.Ne=new A.ac("Five of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83e\udd76","Financial hardship, poverty, and isolation. Difficult times are here, but support may be closer than it seems.","Recovery, spiritual poverty, or accepting help. Beginning to emerge from a difficult period.")
B.Nq=new A.ac("Six of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83e\udd32","Generosity, charity, and sharing wealth. The cycle of giving and receiving is in beautiful balance.","Strings attached, power imbalance, or selfishness. Generosity may come with hidden conditions.")
B.Nn=new A.ac("Seven of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udf31","Hard work, patience, and long-term vision. You have planted seeds \u2014 now wait and tend them with care.","Impatience, poor investment, or lack of reward. Effort may not be yielding the expected results.")
B.Nd=new A.ac("Eight of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83d\udd28","Diligence, skill development, and craftsmanship. Focus on honing your craft through dedicated work.","Perfectionism, mediocrity, or lack of focus. Going through the motions without passion or growth.")
B.Na=new A.ac("Nine of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udf3f","Luxury, self-sufficiency, and independence. You have worked hard and now enjoy the fruits of your labor.","Over-investment in work, financial setback, or false success. True contentment may be missing.")
B.Ob=new A.ac("Ten of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udfe1","Legacy, family wealth, and long-term fulfillment. Everything built over time now comes to lasting fruition.","Family disputes, financial failure, or fleeting success. The foundation may have cracks.")
B.NJ=new A.ac("Page of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83d\udcda","Ambition, diligence, and a new practical venture. A student of life eager to learn and build something real.","Lack of progress, procrastination, or get-rich-quick thinking. Dreams without action go nowhere.")
B.NQ=new A.ac("Knight of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83d\udc02","Hard work, routine, and reliability. A steady, methodical approach will get you where you want to go.","Stubbornness, boredom, or laziness. The routine has become a rut \u2014 something needs to shift.")
B.Nk=new A.ac("Queen of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udf3a","Nurturing, practicality, and financial security. A warm, resourceful presence who creates comfort and abundance.","Smothering, financial dependency, or work-life imbalance. Practicality may come at an emotional cost.")
B.N5=new A.ac("King of Pentacles","Pentacles","\ud83c\udff0","Wealth, business acumen, and security. A steady, successful leader who has mastered the material world.","Greed, materialism, or financial mismanagement. Wealth may be corrupting or poorly handled.")
